channel.title: How do I log in? It tells me to make a server and I do, but it doesn't work
channel.description:
I log in with my username and password, but then it tells me to click cancel and hit create server. I do this, and then it says that the server was crated successfully, then I try again to log in, and it tells me to create a server, again. Why does it do this, and why can't I log in?
The ip thing it'll say like ##.#.##.##, do I need to change this to log in? And if I do, can you post one I can use to just play? >_>
(First time here.)
